  "prompt": "Is there any good institute for differently abled child near Noida areas?",
  "response": "Yes, there are several institutes and centers near Noida that cater to the needs of differently-abled children. Some of them include:\n\n1. **The Pathways School Noida**: They have an inclusive approach and support children with special needs.\n\n2. **Step by Step School**: Located in Noida, this school offers an inclusive education system where children with special needs learn alongside their peers.\n\n3. **Sunrise Learning Foundation**: This is an NGO that provides educational and therapeutic services for children with autism and other disabilities. It is located in Noida.\n\n4. **MBCN (Mata Bhagwanti Chadha Niketan)**: Situated in Noida, it is a school dedicated to providing support and education to children with different disabilities.\n\n5. **Tamana Special School**: While it\u2019s a bit farther in Vasant Vihar, Delhi, Tamana is a well-known center for children with autism and other developmental disabilities.\n\n6. **Seth M.R. Jaipuria Schools**: They have a branch in Noida that emphasizes inclusive education.\n\n7. **Pragyan School**: Located in Greater Noida, they provide support for children with special needs, integrating them into their inclusive schooling system.\n\nIt's always a good idea to visit these centers, speak with the staff, and understand their approach to see which institution aligns best with the specific needs of the child.",
